metadata.name: Into the blue
metadata.description:
Beneath the ocean's azure veil they dance,
Colorful fish, a vibrant cosmic trance.
Amongst blue hard corals, their kingdom's thrones,
A tropical reef where beauty ever roams.

Their scales, a tapestry of hues so bold,
Like artists' brushstrokes, stories yet untold.
Emerald greens and golds, a shimmering fire,
Crimson and sapphire, a heavenly attire.

They glide with grace through nature's kaleidoscope,
Unveiling secrets as they dive and elope.
A symphony of life, a visual delight,
Where dreams take flight beneath the sun's warm light.

Oh, vibrant fish, your vivid shades embrace,
A testament to nature's wondrous grace.
In this reef's sanctuary, an endless play,
Where colors bloom and dreams will always stay.
